      "writtenOn": "2019-12-09T19:49:48Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Let’s not defeat the type system while we’re doing this. Why not SECURITY_DESCRIPTOR* for this?\n\nFor that matter, why doesn’t this function or the inner fallback one return SECURITY_DESCRIPTOR*?",
      "revId": "e3188d1aa81a7061486502970c349f6451d693f9",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
